flowRoot.flowPara: Content in each row is vertically
Big listviews can have in each row upto 3 colums: Icon column, Text column, Arrow/Info collumn.
Icon column should only have an icon in it. Text column should have one or two rows of text. Arrow/Info collumn should have either the arrow icon or a text (like remaining time).
Row column size is dependant on it's content plus spacing.
Content in each row is vertically
Medium listviews can have in each row upto 3 colums: Icon column, Text column, Arrow/Info collumn.
Icon column should only have an icon in it. Text column should have one or two rows of text. Arrow/Info collumn should have either the arrow icon or a text (like remaining time).
Row column size is dependant on it's content plus spacing.
Content in each row is vertically
Small listviews can have in each row upto 3 colums: Icon column, Text column, Arrow/Info collumn.
Icon column should only have an icon in it. Text column should have only one row of text. Arrow/Info collumn should have either the arrow icon or a text (like remaining time).
Row column size is dependant on it's content plus spacing.
